        "enunciado_html":  "\u003cdiv style=\"text-align: justify;\"\u003e\n\u003cp style=\"margin-bottom: 0;\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: #00f0ff;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp style=\"text-align: justify;\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: #ffffff;\"\u003ePaciente de 65 anos, em tratamento quimioter\u0026aacute;pico por neoplasia de mama, apresenta quadro s\u0026uacute;bito de choque circulat\u0026oacute;rio. Ao internar na UTI, \u0026eacute; submetido a exame ultrassonogr\u0026aacute;fico pulmonar e card\u0026iacute;aco, cujos achados mais relevantes est\u0026atilde;o ilustrados nas imagens a seguir. Analise as informa\u0026ccedil;\u0026otilde;es e assinale a alternativa com o diagn\u0026oacute;stico mais prov\u0026aacute;vel:\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg style=\"width: 100%; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://medreviewflashcards.s3.sa-east-1.amazonaws.com/questoes_images/f7SuOgN6WOCvSSXk7bYUa7pA94AzTRMXfA4OiBBO.png\" alt=\"Jato de regurgita\u0026ccedil;\u0026atilde;o tric\u0026uacute;spide e dilata\u0026ccedil;\u0026atilde;o do ventr\u0026iacute;culo direito. \" /\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e",
